											<p>
												When you creating an event there will be three dates you have to set. Start Dates & End Dates are set to show the duration of the event
												and will display on your events page as well as in search function. This also effects the count down timer that displays on your events page.
												The "Ticket cut off" date is the last date that customers will be able to purchase tickets.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="accordion-section">
