											</p>
											<ul>
												<li>Start Date & End dates refer to the dates the ticket will be active. The customer will only be able to use the ticket between the selected dates</li>
												<li>Once you have created a ticket you cannot remove it. You will only be able to activate it and de-activate it.</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="accordion-section">
										<a class="accordion-section-header" data-target="#accordion-2">Can I remove a ticket?</a>
										<div id="accordion-2" class="accordion-section-content">
											<p>No. You cannot. This is to protect the customer.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="accordion-section">
										<a class="accordion-section-header" data-target="#accordion-3">Where can I view my ticket sales stats & revenue?</a>
